    public static enum IRegExpLiteralNode.RegExpFlag
extends Enum<IRegExpLiteralNode.RegExpFlag>
    Represents a flag set on a Regular Expression

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      DOTALL
      s - Specifies whether the dot character (.) in a regular expression pattern matches new-line characters.
      EXTENDED
      x - Specifies whether to use extended mode for the regular expression.
      GLOBAL
      g -Specifies whether to use global matching for the regular expression.
      IGNORECASE
      i - Specifies whether the regular expression ignores case sensitivity.
      MULTILINE
      m - If it is set, the caret (^) and dollar sign ($) in a regular expression match before and after new lines.
